      await interaction.reply({
        content: '‚úÖ Y√™u c·∫ßu h·ªó tr·ª£ ƒë√£ ƒë∆∞·ª£c g·ª≠i. Team s·∫Ω ph·∫£n h·ªìi s·ªõm nh·∫•t c√≥ th·ªÉ.',
